      <strong style="color: #333333;">Edit Your Profile</strong><br> Describe your personal interests, work experience & contact info.
      <%= link_to 'Complete now!', wizard_url, {style: 'color: #74CCD1; text-decoration: none;'} %>
    </td>
  </tr>
